:"تشظّى اللُّوْلُوُ عَنِ الصَّدَفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The pearls became separated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scattered, from the oyster-shells"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) See also 1, in two places."}],"source_refs":["A","Msb","K","TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}